headline: Here’s Americans’ Favorite Tax-Prep Service. It Isn’t the Biggest.
summary: A new survey from J.D. Power suggests that the increasing sophistication and ease-of-use of do-it-yourself tax programs is putting pressure on professional tax preparers.
